94
00:06:28,782 --> 00:06:30,081
Aku tidak perlu menggantinya.

95
00:06:30,082 --> 00:06:31,953
- Terima kasih. - Baiklah.

96
00:06:32,823 --> 00:06:34,123
Jun Woo.

97
00:06:35,493 --> 00:06:36,492
Ya?

98
00:06:36,493 --> 00:06:38,362
