142
00:08:52,222 --> 00:08:56,263
Baiklah, Anak-anak. Kelas telah dimulai.

143
00:08:56,492 --> 00:08:58,701
Pil Sang, lepaskan Chan Yeol.

144
00:08:58,702 --> 00:09:00,863
Gyu Nam, pisahkan mereka.

145
00:09:01,803 --> 00:09:04,601
Da Heen, ini waktunya belajar.

146
00:09:04,602 --> 00:09:06,172
Kamu selalu mengantuk karena terus kelaparan.

147
00:09:06,173 --> 00:09:07,302
Da Heen!

148
00:09:07,303 --> 00:09:09,072
Soo Bin, bangunkan dia.

149
00:09:09,842 --> 00:09:11,812
Anak-anak, ayo belajar.

