175
00:10:44,132 --> 00:10:47,503
Aku wali kelasmu. Hormati aku, ya?

176
00:10:48,443 --> 00:10:49,843
Aku kasihan kepadanya.

177
00:10:50,673 --> 00:10:52,343
Itu sangat menyedihkan.

178
00:10:52,482 --> 00:10:53,782
