190
00:11:51,202 --> 00:11:53,442
Aku wali kelas mereka. Aku orang dewasa.

191
00:11:58,913 --> 00:12:00,312
Baiklah.

192
00:12:01,443 --> 00:12:02,713
Maaf, Anak-anak.

193
00:12:05,252 --> 00:12:07,383
Ayo kita mulai.

194
00:12:08,423 --> 00:12:11,322
